---

<Layout
  title="Position Size Calculator | CryptoCalk"
  description="Free position size calculator for crypto traders. Determine optimal trade size based on your account balance, risk tolerance, and stop-loss. Supports leverage up to 125x."
  lang="en"
  pageType="calculator"
